## New Project: replica
- **Replaces:** mitchellh/copystructure (Go, 1,558 importers, 357 stars)
- **Why:** Archived July 2024, last release Apr 2022. Single maintainer (mitchellh) moved on from Go. Depends on mitchellh/reflectwalk (also archived, 1,503 importers). Pre-generics interface{} API, global mutable state (Copiers/ShallowCopiers maps), no cycle detection. Fragmented alternatives: tiendc/go-deepcopy (167 stars), brunoga/deep (110 stars) — none with traction.
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/replica (verified available on pkg.go.dev)
- **Improvements:** generics Copy[T], cycle detection, functional options (no global state), inlined reflectwalk, compatibility layer, zero dependencies
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #670 (scaffolding), #671 (core Copy/Must), #672 (options/tags), #673 (compat layer), #674 (tests)

